<h1>Nginx rewrite</h1>

<p>2014-01-26 00:47 Sunday</p>

<p><a href="http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_rewrite_module.html" target="_blank">http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_rewrite_module.html</a></p>

<p><a href="http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/ngx_http_rewrite_module.html" target="_blank">http://nginx.org/en/docs/http/converting_rewrite_rules.html</a></p>

<p>2014-01-09 00:10 Thursday 近日全面转战 Nginx 以支持 yeoman 项目的静态输出和 express</p>

<p>以下文件为 ~/www_apache/api/.htaccess 的内容</p>

<pre>
###
### For Apache
###
#RewriteEngine On
#RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php [L];

###
### For Nginx
###
if (!-f $request_filename) {
	rewrite ^/(.*)$ /api/index.php last;
}</pre>

<h2>WordPress&#39; .htaccess</h2>

<p>2014-01-26 01:02 Sunday 去淑芬家上网</p>

<pre>
    server {
        listen      80;
        server_name wordpress;
        root            /Users/mlhch/www_apache/wordpress/;
        include         /Users/mlhch/www_apache/wordpress/.htaccess;

        location / {
            index           index.html;
        }

        # pass the PHP scripts to FastCGI server listening on 127.0.0.1:9000
        #
        location ~ \.php$ {
            root            /Users/mlhch/www_apache/wordpress/;
            fastcgi_pass    127.0.0.1:50000;
            fastcgi_index   index.php;
            fastcgi_param   SCRIPT_FILENAME  $document_root$fastcgi_script_name;
            include         fastcgi_params;
        }
    }</pre>

<p>.htaccess</p>

<pre>
if (!-e $request_filename) {
    rewrite ^/(.*)$ /index.php last;
}</pre>
